nitial purchase.<\/p>\n<div>\n<p>A carrying case is included.<\/p>\n<p>Sizes:&nbsp; (up to)&nbsp; 120&#8243; x 120\u2033<\/p>\n<h5><a href=\"\/seg-banner-wall\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PRODUCT SHEET<\/a><\/h5>\n<\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"section-4f1fe65-2\" class=\"gem-tta-panel \" data-vc-content=\".gem-tta-panel-body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gem-tta-panel-heading\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"gem-tta-panel-title gem-tta-controls-icon-position-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#section-4f1fe65-2\" data-vc-accordion data-vc-container=\".gem-tta-container\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"gem-tta-title-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tBranded Promotion Table\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"gem-tta-controls-icon gem-tta-controls-icon-opened\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"gem-tta-controls-icon gem-tta-controls-icon-closed\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gem-tta-panel-body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gem-text-output\"><p>A branded table at the tradeshow or event will be a conversation location to close a sale. Our Promotion Table is branded on 3 sides and comes with a built-in shelf in the rear for storage of collateral.<\/p><p>It sets up in minutes from it\u2019s own traveling bag. Pair this light-weight, impactful table with our other tradeshow products like the Quick Display Curved, Velcro Wall Banner, Adjustable Wall Banner or the SEG Wall Banner.<\/p><p>Graphics are easily replaced, for a new look in minutes.<\/p><div><p>The size: 39.5\u2033 W x 12\u2033D x 40\u2033 H<\/p><h5><a href=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Promotion-Table.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PRODUCT SHEET<\/a><\/h5><\/div><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"section-4f1fe65-3\" class=\"gem-tta-panel \" data-vc-content=\".gem-tta-panel-body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gem-tta-panel-heading\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"gem-tta-panel-title gem-tta-controls-icon-position-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#section-4f1fe65-3\" data-vc-accordion data-vc-container=\".gem-tta-container\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"gem-tta-title-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAdjustable Banner Stand\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"gem-tta-controls-icon gem-tta-controls-icon-opened\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"gem-tta-controls-icon gem-tta-controls-icon-closed\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gem-tta-panel-body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gem-text-output\"><p>Not all backdrops are created equal. The JVI adjustable wall is durable, light-weight and easy to setup. The fact that it is adjustable allows you to choose a size to fit your event requirement. The high quality, dye-sub fabric stretches tight to reveal a professional looking backdrop for any occasion.<\/p><p>It comes with a convenient carrying case.<\/p><p>Size: 48\u2033 x 120\u2033<\/p><h5><a href=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/JN5_-Adjustable-Wall-Banner-1.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PRODUCT SHEET<\/a><\/h5><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id