ta-panel-body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gem-tta-panel-heading\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"gem-tta-panel-title gem-tta-controls-icon-position-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#section-4f1fe65-6\" data-vc-accordion data-vc-container=\".gem-tta-container\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"gem-tta-title-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tSEG WALL DISPLAYS FRONT OR BACKLIT\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"gem-tta-controls-icon gem-tta-controls-icon-opened\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"gem-tta-controls-icon gem-tta-controls-icon-closed\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gem-tta-panel-body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gem-text-output\"><p>If you require a wall display that has high impact and can be changed out easily and affordably JVI has the answer for you. It is our SEG framing system. It is custom made to your design. See examples to the left.<\/p><p>The frame is made from lightweight yet sturdy aluminum, assembled using a simple connector system. It can be custom designed or shaped to fit any space. The display\u00a0can be wall mounted, freestanding, suspended, retro-fitted or used to build an entire structure. It can be single sided, double sided or cubed; teamed with LED lighting, backlit or spotlit\u00a0and can securely support LED TVs or iPads. It can be assembled for a one-off event, reused time and time again, or fixed in place in an office or retail environment.<\/p><p>The artwork is printed on stretch fabric selected from our unique range of purpose<br \/>made fabrics that allow you to achieve any look in any space, seamlessly up to 10\u2019<br \/>high x any length. The silicone gasket fitted to the fabric border ensures an easy to<br \/>insert, taut finish.<\/p><h5><a href=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/3x3-LED-Modular.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PRODUCT SHEET<\/a><\/h5><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"section-4f1fe65-7\" class=\"gem-tta-panel \" data-vc-content=\".gem-tta-panel-body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gem-tta-panel-heading\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"gem-tta-panel-title gem-tta-controls-icon-position-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#section-4f1fe65-7\" data-vc-accordion data-vc-container=\".gem-tta-container\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"gem-tta-title-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tVELCRO FREE STANDING WALL\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"gem-tta-controls-icon gem-tta-controls-icon-opened\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"gem-tta-controls-icon gem-tta-controls-icon-closed\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gem-tta-panel-body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gem-text-output\"><p>Free Standing Walls can be made from our framing system to meet the requirements you have from a space or design perspective. One of the examples shown in the slide show is a Pop Up Wall Banner system that employs the same framing and graphics. This is a product that is available in two sizes. However, we can make free standing walls to fit your specific needs.<\/p><p>These walls can be custom designed to fit any space. It can be single sided, double sided or cubed; teamed with LED lighting, backlit or spotlit. It can securely support LED TVs or iPads. It can be assembled for a one off event, reused time and time again, or fixed in place in an office or retail environment.<\/p><p>The artwork is printed on stretch fabric selected from our unique range of purpose made fabrics that allow you to achieve any look in any space, seamlessly up to 10\u2019 high x any length. The silicone gasket fitted to the fabric border ensures an easy to insert, taut finish.<\/p><h5><a href=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/SEG-Wall-Banner.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PRODUCT SHEET<\/a><\/h5><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div id=\"section-4f1fe65-8\" class=\"gem-tta-panel \" data-vc-content=\".gem-tta-panel-body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gem-tta-panel-heading\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"gem-tta-panel-title gem-tta-controls-icon-position-left\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"#section-4f1fe65-8\" data-vc-accordion data-vc-container=\".gem-tta-container\">\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"gem-tta-title-text\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tBacklit Wall\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"gem-tta-controls-icon gem-tta-controls-icon-opened\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-minus\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"gem-tta-controls-icon gem-tta-controls-icon-closed\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<i aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"fas fa-plus\"><\/i>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gem-tta-panel-body\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"gem-text-output\"><p>Backlit graphic displays are high impact and get noticed. Making a graphics change can be expensive and require special tools, not with the JVI system. JVI\u2019s \u00a0SEG framing system is custom made to your backlit design. See examples to the left.<\/p><p>The frame is made from lightweight yet sturdy aluminum, assembled using a simple connector system. It can be custom designed or shaped to fit any space. It can be wall mounted, freestanding, suspended, retro-fitted or used to build an entire structure. It can be single or double sided, and teamed with LED lighting\u00a0for a brilliant backlit graphic.<\/p><p>The artwork is printed on stretch fabric selected from our unique range of purpose<br \/>made fabrics that allow you to achieve any look in any space, seamlessly up to 10\u2019<br \/>high x any length. A\u00a0silicone gasket sewn into the fabric border fits\u00a0into a channel on the hardware frame which ensures a taut image with no wrinkles.<\/p><h5><a href=\"\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/Backlit-Plinko-Wall_ll.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">PRODUCT SHEET<\/a><\/h5><h5><a href=\"\/double-sided-seg-backlit-setup\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">SETUP DEMO VIDEO<\/a><\/h5><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-50 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-0d6dd7c\" data-id=\"0d6dd7c\" data-element_type=\"column\" data-e-type=\"column\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2c2e492 flex-horizontal-align-default flex-horizontal-align-tablet-default flex-horizontal-align-mobile-default flex-vertical-align-default flex-vertical-align-tablet-default flex-vertical-align-mobile-default elementor-widget elementor-widget-thegem-styledbutton\" data-id=\"2c2e492\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;thegem_button_skin&qu